Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:03.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:11.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让她知道知道我们浅贺商业街的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:12.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:16.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:18.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:20.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都是 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 这回要让你见识见识什么叫天罗地网
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:24.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}目标在二丁目的十字路口向左跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:26.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我快受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:28.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很想用能力揍飞他们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:31.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但要是让雏知道的话就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:33.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:35.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,往这边跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:37.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是追丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.98,0:00:39.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.43,0:00:41.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们还是应该找警察…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:42.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:45.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是非要找他们帮忙我还不如咬舌自尽算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:46.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,诗子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:00:59.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这儿
