Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:12.30,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:19.40,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の面影思い出す　ふとした時に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:40.48,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思い出の中　微笑んでるその横顔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:46.16,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}何気ない日々が　大切なんだと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:51.01,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}思う気持ち　それに今気付いたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.82,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と笑って過ごした日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:56.63,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と言い合って泣いた日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:00.99,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君と過ごした日々　愛しい日々
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:03.76,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}大切だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:09.19,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}ねえ　どれだけ離れているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:15.44,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君の温もり思い出しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:20.25,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遠くに見えるあの街の灯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:24.74,hinamatsuri_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}君は笑えてるかな
Comment: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:12.30,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们究竟相距多远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:19.40,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:40.48,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在记忆之中 你微笑着的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:46.16,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡无奇的日常 是无可替的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:51.01,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}这份思念之情 现在终于意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.82,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你欢笑度过的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:56.63,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你争论泪流的曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:00.99,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们携手的每一天 令人无比怜爱的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:03.76,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:09.19,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我们究竟相距多远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:15.44,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回忆起你的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:20.25,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遥遥可见的那条街道的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:24.74,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}你正展露着笑容吗
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:42.55,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(960,0)}第三话 流浪者生活之入门篇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:40.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是被黑社会给盯上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,被盯上？ 应该没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:43.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:45.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还挺担心的 这就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是个流浪汉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是你的前辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:52.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你也被别人追着跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的做法不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:00.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,偷东西是犯法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:03.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种行为是会被抓起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你有其他办法生存吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请你告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:11.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 跟我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:17.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看一下找零钱的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:21.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,10元啊 第一次捡就有运气还真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这下边也用棒子找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:32.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的话 就再去捡罐子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,行 装满了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:39.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这些罐子该怎么处理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们去把这些换成钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还要走多长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:49.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们这些流浪者是要经常走路的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,估计还要走两小时吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么非要做这些事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:56.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟个傻瓜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:00.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你要过原来那种生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得能靠犯罪活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这些一共是690元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:20.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有这个 再去店里就不会被追着跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:21.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这也能买3、4桶你刚才吃的泡面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:26.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:28.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可我这一天走了这么久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:31.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,赚钱可是很不容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:36.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在明白偷东西为什么会被追了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天必须要给你办个欢迎会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:46.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就用你今天赚的钱给大家买酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:50.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让他们接受你这个同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,流浪者就是要互相帮助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:58.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,除了今天我教你的 他们也会教你很多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以把这些钱当作是学费
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了安叔 这孩子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:08.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,重 她叫杏 今后就是我们中的一员了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什么啊 这小鬼怎么过得了这种生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,先观察她一段时间嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:20.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子用今天赚的钱 给大家买了酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你让我喝那我就喝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:31.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,收这么一个小孩子 安叔是怎么想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:34.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是出了事 警察会盯上咱们的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看 大家肯定都这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:40.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,重 还是先喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么 好像我就不能待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是我买的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:50.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样还不如我一个人呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 好不容易开个酒会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唱首歌来听听嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:56.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要唱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:59.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 什么都干不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:02.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？ 连买酒的钱都是我出的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:06.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这些就估计要两千块了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是安叔把不够的部分垫上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你有熟悉的歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 就会一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:25.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那能让大叔们听听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:43.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狼饿着肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:48.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到小鹿它就吃吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:52.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到小猪它就吃吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:57.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,它就吃吃吃 吃吃吃吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吃到撑肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:05.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是我唱得太好听把你们给感动了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:10.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 你唱得 真是难听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:10.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起了我的孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个很爱唱歌的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:18.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 抱歉 刚才对你的态度很差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喝点饮料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么你也哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:38.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:49.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是杏子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:51.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么没回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:59.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还挺喜欢在这里生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:01.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢这种生活？你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 就是打发打发时间而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这打发时间还挺高级的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能吃饱饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:13.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就带了四万
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就先给你吧 记得好好吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:23.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,四 四 四万…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:28.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别 别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会要你的施舍的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:36.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要自己赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:41.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,铁跟铝的价格都跌了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:46.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,钱越来越不好赚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 不知道能不能挨过今年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:56.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她这么精神 应该没什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:09:00.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 好像有人在后面追我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:07.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:13.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:27.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然之间又想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.74,0:09:32.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我原本就打算给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你想干什么 拿去花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那小鬼还在鞠着躬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有了这些钱 大家就可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,终于抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在有钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我以后会付钱买东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:20.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的损失加起来一共是39340元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:22.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,找你零钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我们就放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:25.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再做这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:33.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 你不用关心这些事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把钱全还上了 也挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:41.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说得对啊 不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:47.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们这群人要是有了钱 就全都拿去买酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你也没了后顾之忧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就能开始全新的流浪汉生活了吧
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:04.01,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs90\pos(1408,682)\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&}超能力女儿
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.43,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(860,0)\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1396,502)}超能力女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:08.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早上好 我是三岛瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,秋田县部分地区在除夕举行的民俗活动是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:13.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是生剥鬼节
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:14.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是生剥鬼节
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么说有点自吹自擂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我在学校里的确是个认真的优等生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那只是我白天的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有个小秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:28.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:32.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一到晚上 我就会成为调酒师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要问这是为什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:39.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你穿这身衣服很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你什么时候能来工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是我特地准备给你的嘛 来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我穿上看看我才穿上的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我会付你时薪1500日元的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这对于普通的中学生来说可是很离谱的工资哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:01.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先对于普通的中学生而言打工就很离谱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:04.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:10.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,把这张照片寄给你学校的话 会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:12.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什什什…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:18.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想闹出大问题的话就老实地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:22.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\bord0\c&H807E83&\frz2.013\pos(530,250)}录音 新建录音001
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是我特地准备给你的嘛 来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:24.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:27.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我有不祥的预感 就开了录音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:30.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真有你的 小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近被卷进去的事有点多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:33.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经学乖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:34.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:37.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不互相留下把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要一起把数据都删了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不再威胁我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再威胁你了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:50.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我把衣服换回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:03.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,照片我早就传到电脑去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您的代基里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:08.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,综上所述 我开始了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:13.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:15.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完全超越诗子小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的赞美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:21.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是该笑的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,教导主任 我们也差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:28.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你再说什么的 松谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:29.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚现在才开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:31.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一个不错的酒吧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:32.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再喝下去对身体不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:34.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想早点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,关于明年的年级主任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:39.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我跟校长强烈推荐你的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必让我陪同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:44.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,松谷老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:52.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要死要死要死 怎么办怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗 小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:58.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,实 实际上是因为班主任来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:01.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,船到桥头自然直啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:03.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个 给我来杯马提尼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:06.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:08.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:10.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:11.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:15.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.79,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs80\3c&HB7B4BD&\shad5\bord4\b1\blur3\c&H342F30&\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\b0\4c&H848289&}为了不暴露自己 在努力地变脸中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:24.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太年轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:27.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 感觉超级眼熟的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:31.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三 三岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:36.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,请 请给我一杯百万富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 冷静下来 好险！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:40.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说都不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:41.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我难道醉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我教的学习认真的乖学生居然在做调酒师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:46.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:49.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太吓人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:53.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,松谷老师 超怀疑我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 松谷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这个调酒师稍微 不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是相当像我教的一个学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你可糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:09.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真的 你年级主任的事就要吹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:12.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊是我认错啦 还真有长得像的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:14.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:17.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看都只是中学生而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:21.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥 你喝了就懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么可是中学生调得出来的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小瞳可是超强的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:28.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,三岛她好像名字就是叫瞳…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:31.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你个该死的蠢跟班仔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,行吧既然都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:36.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我从学生时代开始就在各式各样的酒吧工作过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我对味道可是很挑剔的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:43.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就让他见识一下吧 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:45.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:08.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您的百万富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,了 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是完美的摇酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:26.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没了解到她的搅拌技术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:29.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才稍微观察了一下她的手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她的手还没有吧勺茧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说她虽然摇酒的技术还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但搅拌的火喉还远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那您请下单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:44.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 那就来一杯调酒师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您的调酒师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:06.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:10.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这等技术 在银座一流的店里也相当少见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且居然还没有吧勺茧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就做得太多把茧弄没了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这确实是中学生做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:27.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:31.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今后请务必继续让我品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:33.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:35.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了俘虏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:47.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,P.S. 瞒着父母开的账户
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:51.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以惊人的气势进着钱 稍微让我有点害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:18:00.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田你那边的肉丸多了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:01.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,前阵子我遇到了杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:11.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要也学学杏子试试流浪生活？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 跟你比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和她一起住要好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:22.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:24.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还要再带我来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:26.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 已经开始想下次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:29.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(276,800)\fs65\shad0\bord2\blur2\fn思源黑体 CN Regular\c&H342F30&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(738,630)}肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:31.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,行行好吧 行行好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:30.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}呐 接下来想吃甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田你那边的肉丸比较少哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是因为你昨天抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你可以拿走多出的那一个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:48.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:53.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天有会面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:55.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这是什么情况！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:21.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 怎么会 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:22.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是我打扫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:26.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了新田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:28.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么不开心的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这蠢货 眼泪这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:35.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,开心的时候也会流出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 买下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:13.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 要是再打碎的话我真的会干死你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:15.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,别打碎 绝对不能打碎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:24.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 这边等下再打扫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:42.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8)\fn新蒂小丸子\fs100\bord4\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H6E5C50&}奖励雏时使用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:51.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,奖励时用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:55.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也好好努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:56.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,准备作为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的晚饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得和以往的味道不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:08.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了新田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:12.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就是今天雏好像有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反常地把多出来的菜让给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:17.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门的时候也特地到玄关来送我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:20.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就是说雏也有所成长了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:24.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天得奖她顿好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:28.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都有备好奖励用的鲑鱼子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她都没做出值得表扬的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:32.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都放坏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:50.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 肚子好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:55.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:02.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也要奖励她一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:05.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
